name: AppSync Unified
shortDescription: Enables the ability to install unsigned/fakesigned iOS applications.
author: Linus Yang, Karen／明美

users.issues: DO NOT INSTALL FROM APPADDICT REPO!!!!! It will not fully install and will be a complete pain in the ass to fix your jailbreak. If you are stupid like I was and install it, to fix it is to go into filza, search in root ‘AppSyncunified’ everything that pops up that is for the tweak delete, and go back into cydia and you will be able to uninstall it, and install tweaks again.
Does not work on iPad Air 2, ios 11.3.1
Cydia installer crashed, had to force reboot
Apps signed only with ldid don’t work
